Because **Dynamic Web Module 3.0 requires Java 1.6 or newer**. (*Dynamic Web Module version 3.0 refer Serverlet 3.0*)&lt;br/&gt;
You should &lt;br/&gt;
* Download and install newer JDK ([JDK 1.8u20][1]) &lt;br/&gt;
